content:
When an agent begins a customer Live Chat or Messaging session, Einstein analyzes the chat as it unfolds and drafts replies from context or based on the Salesforce org's unique Knowledge base. Agents can then post replies to customers with one click or edit and polish them before posting.

Available in Lightning Experience, Enterprise, and Unlimited Editions with the Einstein for Service add-on. Available in French, German, Italian, Japanese, and Spanish.

To set up: Personalize customer service and save agent's time in just a few steps. Replies appear in the Einstein Replies component of the Chat and Messaging tab in the Lightning Service Console. Einstein recommends replies when your customer sends the first message in a chat or messaging session.

Service Replies charges only for the activity you use. Track usage against subscription allowance.
title: Einstein Service Replies for Chat Setup
